<!-- Itemo -->
<section id="itemo" class="py-12 sm:py-16 bg-charcoal-900">
    <div class="max-w-7xl mx-auto px-4 sm:px-8">
        <div class="mb-6 sm:mb-8">
            <div class="text-accent-500 font-medium mb-2 text-sm">PEER-TO-PEER MARKETPLACE</div>
            <h2 class="text-2xl sm:text-3xl font-bold text-white mb-3 sm:mb-4">Itemo — Peer-to-Peer Rental Marketplace</h2>
            <p class="text-base sm:text-lg text-charcoal-200 max-w-3xl">
                A peer-to-peer borrowing and rental platform designed to allow users to safely lend and rent everyday items. Developed from initial concept through to a fully production-ready platform, including mobile apps, payments, identity verification, and complex rental workflows.
            </p>
        </div>

        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-4 sm:gap-8 mb-8 sm:mb-12">
            <div class="bg-charcoal-800 border border-charcoal-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-2">THE CHALLENGE</div>
                <p class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">Peer-to-peer marketplaces carry inherent risk: payments between strangers, identity verification, fraud prevention, and complex lifecycle state management. Early prototypes validated the idea, but production required a complete rethink around security and reliability.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-charcoal-800 border border-charcoal-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-2">THE APPROACH</div>
                <p class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">Rebuilt with a production-first mindset. Designed auditable rental state transitions, integrated Stripe with careful webhook handling, implemented KYC checks, and built AI-powered search. Delivered a single coherent platform across web, iOS, Android, and admin tooling.</p>
            </div>
            <div class="bg-charcoal-800 border border-charcoal-700 p-4 sm:p-6 rounded-lg">
                <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-2">THE OUTCOME</div>
                <p class="text-charcoal-100 text-sm sm:text-base">A fully production-ready marketplace platform with secure payment flows, identity verification, clear operational tooling via an admin dashboard, and a system designed to evolve without rewrites.</p>
            </div>
        </div>

        <div>
            <div class="text-sm text-charcoal-400 mb-3">KEY CAPABILITIES</div>
            <div class="flex flex-wrap gap-2">
                <span class="bg-charcoal-700 text-charcoal-200 px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs sm:text-sm">End-to-end product delivery</span>
                <span class="bg-charcoal-700 text-charcoal-200 px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs sm:text-sm">Payments & KYC</span>
                <span class="bg-charcoal-700 text-charcoal-200 px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs sm:text-sm">Trust-sensitive system design</span>
                <span class="bg-charcoal-700 text-charcoal-200 px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs sm:text-sm">Complex business workflows</span>
                <span class="bg-charcoal-700 text-charcoal-200 px-3 py-1 rounded text-xs sm:text-sm">Web + mobile delivery</span>
            </div>
        </div>
    </div>
</section>

<!-- Wulse -->
